Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:11.42,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\pos(854,718)}什么是睡袋？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.34,0:00:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.96,0:00:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}是登山用品店！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.81,0:00:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这种店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.92,0:00:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些杂乱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是宝贝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.26,0:00:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有炊具呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.96,0:00:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钛钢！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好轻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.20,0:00:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Schlafsack是…睡袋的意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人！ 七万！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好贵 还这么薄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个子好高
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身材也好 好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我们一间学校的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我参谋一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件一万八的睡袋 和这件两万四的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.47,0:00:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该买哪件好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.44,0:00:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我也不是内行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 下次我想背着帐篷和睡袋来一次纵走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:04.54,yama_neta,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}纵走登山：区别于往返山脚和山顶之间的登山方式\N纵走是从一座山顶前往下一座山顶 攀登多座山峰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.99,0:01:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纵走？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.38,0:01:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在山里 连登多座山峰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.95,0:01:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 就不知道怎么选睡袋了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.85,0:01:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡袋又有什么区别呢
