Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.86,0:01:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一背就是一整天 重量非常重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.59,0:01:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有做兼职攒钱 但预算比预想的还紧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然犹豫不决 大概是想买那件贵的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说她会高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.88,0:01:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其妥协让步 宁愿后悔也要一步到位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.45,0:01:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也这么想！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.61,0:01:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 让我作出决定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.33,0:01:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就买
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.98,0:01:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知有没有让她满意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要爬山吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然犹豫了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要爬山！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不由自主就说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们就是驴友了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们交换电邮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫斋藤枫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.23,0:02:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小葵 她是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.13,0:02:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是我们学校的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我啊 不是很擅长与人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊 你现在还提这个干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 好直截了当
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢 你有自知之明不就很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小枫姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.91,0:02:51.75,phone_message,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz341.5\pos(686,114)}上次谢谢你哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看 小枫姐给我发邮件了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又交到了一个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}行こう！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}スタッカートみたいに 胸を叩くワクワク感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}不思議　不安より
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}楽しみの容量が増えたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}また明日！やっほー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}昂扬感像断奏音符般拍打胸膛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}真奇妙 不但没有不安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}快乐的容量反而更大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}明天再见！YAHOO
